name: X_VERSIONED_OBJECT
title: X_VERSIONED_OBJECT
description: Variety of Extract content that consists is a sharable data-oriented version of `VERSIONED_OBJECT<T>`.

element.short: Variety of Extract content that consists is a sharable data-oriented version of `VERSIONED_OBJECT<T>`.
element.definition: Variety of Extract content that consists is a sharable data-oriented version of `VERSIONED_OBJECT<T>`.

element.short: Owner_id from original `VERSIONED_OBJECT`, which identifies source EHR.
element.definition: Owner_id from original `VERSIONED_OBJECT`, which identifies source EHR.

element.short: Total number of versions in original `VERSIONED_OBJECT` at time of creation of this `X_VERSIONED_OBJECT`.
element.definition: Total number of versions in original `VERSIONED_OBJECT` at time of creation of this `X_VERSIONED_OBJECT`.

element.short: The number of Versions in this extract for this Versioned object, i.
element.definition: The number of Versions in this extract for this Versioned object, i.e. the count of items in the versions attribute. May be 0 if only revision history is requested.

element.short: Optional revision history of the original `VERSIONED_OBJECT`.
element.definition: Optional revision history of the original `VERSIONED_OBJECT`. If included, it is the complete revision history.

element.short: 0 or more Versions from the original `VERSIONED_OBJECT`, according to the Extract specification.
element.definition: 0 or more Versions from the original `VERSIONED_OBJECT`, according to the Extract specification.
